\cf0 \cb2 Joseph Cardoso - JPMorgan Chase & Co, Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Erik Woodring - Morgan Stanley, Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Timothy Long - Barclays Bank PLC, Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Jordan Lyonnais - BofA Securities, Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Joseph Nolan - Longbow Research LLC\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Ivan Feinseth - Tigress Financial Partners LLC, Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Benjamin Bollin - Cleveland Research Company LLC\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Noah Zatzkin - KeyBanc Capital Markets Inc., Research Division\cb1 \
